                     IO | IQ | IR | IS | IT | JM | JO | JP | KE | KG | 
                     KH | KI | KM | KN | KP | KR | KW | KY | KZ | LA | 
                     LB | LC | LI | LK | LR | LS | LT | LU | LV | LY | 
                     MA | MC | MD | MG | MH | MK | ML | MM | MN | MO | 
