                     VU | WF | WS | YE | YT | YU | ZA | ZM | ZW) #IMPLIED 
>

<!-- Status of the issue -->
<!ELEMENT comment (description)>
<!ATTLIST comment
	by CDATA #REQUIRED
	date CDATA #REQUIRED
>
<!ELEMENT description (%text-elts; | %block-elts; | %single-block-elts;)*>
